name: com.ageoflearning.kraken-ioc
description:
This is a source code version of KrakenIoc that allows KrakenIoc DI containers to work with Unity inspector as a Unity package.
KrakenIoc is made by Age of Learning, and is available at https://github.com/AgeOfLearning/kraken-ioc

Check the changelog for version equivalents between this Unity package and the original pure C# KrakenIoc APIs.
